The Death-Song of Kulan Gath: A Dream of Bitter Ash
Avengers (1998) #3
results.description: Captain America must train his newly-freed friends to act in an Iron Man-lead attack on Morgan. But when the heroes are forced to battle their ensorcelled teammates, will they be willing to see this battle to the end?

results.title: The Death-Song of Kulan Gath: Conclusion!
Avengers (1998) #31
results.description: The Vision assembles the Avengers to fight the Grim Reaper!

results.title: Avengers (1998) #4
results.description: The Avengers have emerged victorious from their last battle. Now it is time to form the new roster for the superhero team. Who will be chosen? Who will be left out?

results.title: Avengers (1998) #45
results.description: Kang finishes up the preparations for his assault on planet Earth! Meanwhile, the Vision infiltrates the enigmatic Triune Understanding.

results.title: Avengers (1998) #46
results.description: The battle begins! Earth’s Mightiest Heroes split up to defend the world on three fronts, and are taking the fight to Kang himself!

results.title: Avengers (1998) #47
results.description: Warbird is in dire straits! Soon she’ll find an unlikely ally in…the Scarlet Centurion!

results.title: Avengers (1998) #48
results.description: The Avengers continue their valiant fight against Kang the Conqueror and the Master of the World! The U.S. government launches the infamous Sentinels to fight Kang! All this, and the mysterious plan of the Triune Understanding is revealed!

results.title: Let Slip The Dogs of War!
Avengers (1998) #49
results.description: ‘NUFF SAID silent issue! Kang makes his final assault on Washington, DC. Will the Master of the World’s defenses hold out, or is the capital city doomed?

results.title: Avengers (1998) #50
results.description: Captain America, Triathlon, and the rest of the Avengers in space take on the Triune Understanding and the Tri-Evil!

results.title: Avengers (1998) #51
results.description: With Earth now under Kang’s rule, Wonder Man and Scarlet Witch have been imprisoned in a detention camp. Will they be able to pull off a great escape?

results.title: Avengers (1998) #52
results.description: The Avengers break out of captivity! After regrouping at the Master of the World’s compound, the Avengers unlock the secrets of his technology and take the fight back to Kang himself.

results.title: Avengers (1998) #53
results.description: The Avengers and their allies make their final assault on Kang’s Damocles Base. Will Earth’s Mightiest Heroes prevail this time?

results.title: Avengers (1998) #54
results.description: The moment you’ve been waiting for: Captain America versus Kang the Conqueror in single combat.

results.title: Avengers (1998) #55
results.description: As the Avengers mourn those lost in conflict with Kang, Warbird faces a court martial for the murder of the Master of the World.

results.title: Avengers (1998) #56
results.description: The Elements of Doom run wild in St. Louis, and only the Avengers can stop them! But the menace of dozens of power-mad life-forms isn't the only gauntlet the Avengers must run - and it may not even be the worst!

results.title: Avengers (1998) #57
results.description: Mr. Hyde thinks he's tough, and he is - maybe even tough enough to fight the Avengers! But a greater power threatens the Earth itself, which suddenly has a lot fewer people on it!

results.title: Avengers (1998) #58
results.description: The world's leaders have disappeared, and only the Avengers can guide Earth out of chaos! But the path leads to an extradimensional realm ruled by an unexpected adversary!

results.title: Avengers (1998) #59
results.description: Yellowjacket and the Wasp, trapped in extradimensional torment! To rescue them, the Avengers must appeal to a cosmic entity's good side...literally!

results.title: Avengers (1998) #60
results.description: The Avengers vs. Scorpio and the Brotherhood of the Ankh! Will even turning the villains' own forces against them be enough?

results.title: Avengers (1998) #61
results.description: The team gains new international status, but will everyone accept it? Avengers come and go as the new lineup is established and new threats await!

results.title: Avengers (1998) #62
results.description: Jack of Hearts and Ant-Man, two quarrelsome recruits caught in their own crises! One faces his father's secrets, the other his daughter's fate!

results.title: Avengers (1998) #63
results.description: In Eastern Europe, Thor and the Asgardians seek justice - but they may bring war instead, at least if Doctor Doom has his way! Iron Man and Captain America must salvage what they can from a standoff that could shatter the Avengers with a thunder god's hammer!
